dataset.name: ICE Brent Crude Oil, November 2021 (BX2021)
dataset.description:
Contract Size:1,000 barrels

Deliverable Good:The ICE Brent Crude futures contract is a deliverable contract based on EFP delivery with an option to cash settle, i.e the ICE Brent Index price for the day following the last trading day of the futures contract.

Tick Size:US dollars and cents

Pricing Unit:one cent per barrel

Columns: Open, High, Low, Settle, Volume, Previous Day Open Interest. Note that Open Interest is always reported for the previous trading day, to avoid lookahead bias.
